name: Jacoby Online
description: Jacoby Online is a unique reference work bringing together Felix Jacoby’s monumental Die Fragmente der Griechischen Historiker Parts I-III, Brill’s New Jacoby, the new edition of these three parts, and the completely new Parts IV and V. With updates to these products made several times a year, Jacoby Online is destined to be and remain the most authoritive source for the study of the ancient Greek historians.
